                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-145-off797 t18120916-145-cd798"></join>, a copper, value 1 l. 15 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120916-145-victim1217" type="victimName">
